node.text:
July was our slowest month in years, 😔 and I’d be lying if it wasn’t scary, with the state of the world, keeping my head down working has been the only sense of normalcy and lately it just feels harder and harder to reach people out there. 

if you’re out there, say hey 👋🏼 place an order or share our posts with friends. it matters, keeping our doors open keeps the brands we carry in business too. we’re all in this together ❤️

the anxiety small businesses feel right now is heavy to say the least. please if you can support small business with your orders, even small ones make a difference. 

Instagram is hiding posts from your favorite small businesses, ours are barely shared with our organically grown audience,
and now they’re going to be focusing on video sharing rather than photos, hurting so many of us.

if you can, please engage with them on social media and help amplify them. the best way is to save their posts, it’s like a “super like” share their posts in your stories and tag friends, word of mouth is everything 🙏🏼

my shop is surviving but every day I wake up worried my inbox will be empty. I am so lucky to be open still, so many are not. It’s such a heartbreaking time for so many. Things are getting better, the light at the end of the tunnel is here, but we need to make sure small businesses are there on the other side 🌞

Thank you for your continued support of my shop, you in turn support ALL of the small businesses we carry. think about that, that is something 🖤 

PLEASE TAG YOUR FAVORITE SMALL BUSINESSES IN THE COMMENTS 👇🏼

thank you 💓 #shopsmall #shopsmallbusiness #smallbusiness #supportwomenownedbusinesses

node.text:
BIG INVENTORY HEADS UP 😷 

@baggu has stopped wholesale selling of masks to retailers, it's utterly heartbreaking as these were our favorite masks and we know how much our customers loved them. That being said. What is in stock is the last of our inventory, we weren't given any notice and therefore were not able to stock up as we would have liked. 

Head to the site and scoop up what is left, there's a fair amount of kids + adult sets but this is it! 

If you have another favorite brand of adult + kids masks let us know in the comments, we are considering adding another brand in it's place. We do also have adult + kids tie dye mask sets in stock as well.

Community Fundraising Project 🕊🗳
